{"tid":2003485,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"遊行搞手質疑與復課雙重標準","createTime":"2020-05-06T00:20:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T02:45:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0d888323e2529bc8950eaf662ac604082f7ace22","tid":2003485,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T00:20:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200506/INRHM4DVABQVUPMKDJAR6VQEP4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200506%2FINRHM4DVABQVUPMKDJAR6VQEP4%2F&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRMlSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=a73d7980\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200506%2FINRHM4DVABQVUPMKDJAR6VQEP4%2F&h=69ed7e04\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200506/INRHM4DVABQVUPMKDJAR6VQEP4/</a><br />\n<br />\n遊行搞手質疑與復課雙重標準<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200506/large/1588697671_0cac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200506%2Flarge%2F1588697671_0cac.jpg&h=4cf741d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地盤職工總會5.1擺街站遭警員藉限聚令阻撓。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】林鄭月娥昨宣佈放寬限聚令至八人，但堅持不取消限聚令，更聲稱決定不含政治考量。但多名計劃未來一、兩個月搞遊行集會的團體代表批評，既然政府容許學生復課，等同認可恢復社交接觸，沒有理由再延長限聚令，質疑想用限聚令被作政治打壓。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：防暴驅「和你唱」票控行街市民<br />\n<br />\n促還市民集會自由<br />\n<br />\n早已表明今年六四集會不改期的支聯會主席李卓人指，警方以「抱有共同目的」為聚集定義，即使相距1.5米仍.....................義，是「趁疫打壓」，又指政府已經容許多人聚集的中學文憑試開考，5月尾又讓學生復課，反映人群聚集的社交接觸已可以接受。<br />\n<br />\n已入紙申請7.1遊行的民陣召集人岑子杰也認為，如學生在5月底復課，邏輯上不可再限制市民聚集，質疑若政府確實認為社交接觸.................禁制令但又容許復課，則是置學生的安危於不顧。<br />\n<br />\n岑子杰又指限聚令這個「緊箍咒」需要取消，才可還市民遊行集會自由，「從來都唔係四人或八人嘅...............民連四人一組相隔1.5米請願都被票控，所以只要警察唔鍾意，就可以票控你」。<br />\n<br />\n組織5月10日九龍大遊行的民間組織「思穎團隊」正考慮是否因限聚令延長而取消遊行。發起人Swing回應指政府決定娛樂場所重開同樣會..................受社交接觸，同一原則下不應延長限聚令，質疑政府是意圖打壓任何反對政府的遊行集會。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃頌恩"},{"pid":"1c2f1973e6db7b4f324b1a81c6650ae89ae8e4f3","tid":2003485,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T00:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00dfeb42fab2a5cc31f1e18960a4328a88969411","tid":2003485,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T00:23:06.000Z","msg":"三年零八個月"},{"pid":"174bf30c03469a3c4d73c378f89ff51d5b2d6e6f","tid":2003485,"uid":300782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T00:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0796595d03b3e9d1b0fb72d9346cec2017d02e","tid":2003485,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T00:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />識開post"},{"pid":"c23cca1d4652aaedc9671c083061a712c5579dfc","tid":2003485,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T02:45:23.000Z","msg":"Make sense <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}